CurrencyTracker
===============

CurrencyTracker allows you to track your personal collection of world currencies, by tagging the countries that you've visited along your travels.

Added devise gem so need to bundle install,
--------------------------------------------------
bundle 

If database is not created
---------------------------------------------------------
rake db:create 


Run migrations
----------------------------------------------------------
rake db:migrate

Run seed for sample data
----------------------------------------------------------
rake db:seed


Then app
--------------------------------------------------------- 
rails s


